{"tid":1183030,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"守護香港反送中  日期：2019年6月9日 時間：2:30集合；3:00起步 地點：銅鑼灣東角道 至 立法會","createTime":"2019-06-02T15:25:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T20:42:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aac65231fadd60dab1fe209ece17371d1effae5f","tid":1183030,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:25:54.000Z","msg":"民間人權陣線 Civil Human Rights Front <br />\n<br />\n守護香港反送中<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年6月9日<br />\n時間：2:30集合；3:00起步<br />\n地點：銅鑼灣東角道 至 立法會<br />\n<br />\nNo extradition to China, march for our Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nDate: June 9, 2019 (Sun) Time: rally@14:30; march@3:00<br />\nVenue: East Point Road, Causeway Bay -&gt; LegCo<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/60603206_2261822703865108_4329127911094222848_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=982464192ffade75e9f92d048225409d&amp;oe=5D94FC87\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F60603206_2261822703865108_4329127911094222848_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D982464192ffade75e9f92d048225409d%26oe%3D5D94FC87&h=ae76a059&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77bcdd0f4f6b2c01f12eb5aaf84257ce73177ade","tid":1183030,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:26:22.000Z","msg":"嚟緊既星期日"},{"pid":"65841d4b402d631825a4caf6531bc80d07ba1fc0","tid":1183030,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:18:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">最新資訊,  估計好多人,  維園草地起步</span></span><br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線 Civil Human Rights Front<br />\n<br />\n6月9日反「送中」大遊行，最新安排如下：<br />\n<br />\n遊行起點：<span style=\"color: orange;\">銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）</span><br />\n遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n集合時間：2：30PM<br />\n起步時間：3：00PM（或維園草地達八成滿）<br />\n<br />\n參與遊行呼籲：<br />\n<br />\n1. 想與民陣一同起步的遊行參與者，在維園草地集合。<br />\n<br />\n*2. 坐輪椅人士、有需要人士或推嬰兒車的照顧者，可以維園草地旁的「南路」集合，民陣會安排優先出發。<br />\n<br />\n3. 想中途加入遊行的參與者，可在軒尼斯道西行線（往灣仔方向，於銅鑼灣波斯富街之後的路段加入。但必須在帶頭車及遊行帶頭橫額之後，才加入遊行隊伍。）<br />\n<br />\n4. 請所有參與遊行的市民，就長時間遊行做好充足的準備，包括：水、毛巾、手機充電、雨傘、電風扇等等。<br />\n<br />\n無懼政權打壓，6月9日，全港總動員，反「送中」、撤惡法！<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線秘書處<br />\n<br />\n#遊行已獲發不反對通知書<br />\n#警方大石壓死蟹<br />\n#警權無限大<br />\n#人權被出賣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/61620734_2281134285267283_2809325987915890688_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=16575c49eeeb52ed852610bdb4b9c290&amp;oe=5D50D13E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F61620734_2281134285267283_2809325987915890688_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3D16575c49eeeb52ed852610bdb4b9c290%26oe%3D5D50D13E&h=f983196d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.680202458693815/2281134281933950/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2Fphotos%2Fa.680202458693815%2F2281134281933950%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewON5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=b22b54b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.680202458693815/2281134281933950/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"a6d8af42415a7b829e1f9135c11b11e2de18d15b","tid":1183030,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:44:22.000Z","msg":"仲有防曬用品"},{"pid":"1b7c615f14eaa4b5354adbffccc5358223ada686","tid":1183030,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T20:42:16.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣中途加入個位係邊？<br />\n有無街景post黎睇下？"}]}